{"tid":1112501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[球王之歌] 說好的 C朗呢？","createTime":"2019-04-17T12:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T02:58:03.000Z","uid":72652,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"82ecab23b7840f3b0197ba04f0572c61165199b1","tid":1112501,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"*你的射門凌亂著 在最後時刻<br />\n聽著阿積士球迷會歌 甜夢完結了<br />\n情緒莫名的拉扯 終於要輸呢<br />\n而你斷斷續續跑回家 假裝沒事了<br />\n<br />\n時間過了 走了 足球面臨選擇 你冷了 倦了 我哭了<br />\n離開時的不快樂 妳用卡片手寫著 有些愛只給到這 真的痛了<br />\n<br />\n怎麼了 C朗呢 說好的 罰球呢<br />\n眼神呢 遠射呢 盤扭呢 頭搥呢<br />\n開心與不開心一一細數著 你再不捨<br />\n那些贏過的感覺都太深刻 金球不見了<br />\n<br />\n美斯晉了 說好的 宿敵呢<br />\n我錯了 淚乾了 縮腳了 後悔了<br />\n只是祖雲簽的合約還維持著 要怎麼停呢*<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\n怎麼了 你累了 說好的 世盃呢<br />\n你懂了 沒隊友 沒教練 夢遠了你選擇忘了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒入球了 說好的 助攻呢<br />\n我錯了 淚乾了 退隊了 後悔了<br />\n只是回憶的冠軍夢還旋轉著 要怎麼停呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通話好易填<br />\n有冇巴打幫手唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d991c8720ff54e0a8e8cc315acdc1930ea46b8e","tid":1112501,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b11052fb23708ce471ea09424ea9f0a922aeda","tid":1112501,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass